agraph\">The lords of the five kingdoms, who have come from the five worlds to the</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">from the five worlds to the Castle in the Sky, wishing to return to their original worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The lords of the five kingdoms who have moved from the five worlds to the Celestial Castle in hopes of returning to their original worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The &quot;sixth seeker&quot; suddenly appears in the castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the same time, a mysterious dungeon gate also appeared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She has lost her memory, and all she remembers is that she has to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">is that she must go to the abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter the underground gate,\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and then through the Abyss to reach the Abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thus began her journey through the Abyss.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Abyss","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3211460/361c19acaac714029740e4d233533cc4e670f171.jpg"},{"name":"Magical Mix!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3211460/361c19acaac714029740e4d233533cc4e670f171.jpg"},{"name":"Artifact Get!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3211460/361c19acaac714029740e4d233533cc4e670f171.jpg"},{"name":"Hit and Run!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3211460/361c19acaac714029740e4d233533cc4e670f171.jpg"},{"name":"Abyss is out of control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3211460/361c19acaac714029740e4d233533cc4e670f171.jpg"},{"name":"Leaving the Treasure Behind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps